      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FORTUNE HEARTS (1) was well in the market last time but only managed sixth (17.00), beaten 3 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Can atone. PRIORITY ONE (6) isn't a quick beginner but comes home hard and has run into the minors the last three start, the latest winding up strongly when second (19.71) in a Grade 6 at this track. Wound up strongly to place two back then did the same last time, finishing on late when second (19.71) in a Grade 6 at this track. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Overdue and expected to feature again. DREAM CATCH (4) has missed the frame at his last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when second (25.74) at this track in a Grade 6/MDN. Has good speed and can quickly clear the tricky draw. Has the ability and can find best this time. MAYWYN'S QUEEN (8) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
